<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Sep1936"><font color="red">8 September 1936</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): The British edition is now due to come out soon. The queries for the corrections however have only reached up to page 620 odd (out of 780 odd) &hellip; Mr Joyce is away. </div>
